{"tid":390194,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有類似經歷?","createTime":"2017-09-07T01:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T05:18:47.000Z","uid":116421,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"51240db98dfea54d17c98853760389a90674e453","tid":390194,"uid":116421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:41:15.000Z","msg":"細個嘅時候鐘意左當時女友(A) 嘅好朋友 (B)。一年之後同A分左手，同B由朋友關係開始，間中會出下街。但我最後同返A一齊，因為A好依賴我，同A一齊返之前，有向B 表白過，之後B 都有左新男友。<br />\n<br />\n之後好快就中學畢業..大家各散東西..入左U..生活方式同圈子同以前唔同哂..我同A始終都分開左..B 都有其他發展..<br />\n<br />\n之後我再拍過兩三次拖..三年前同左現任女友(C) 一齊..我同C相處好好..都好愛對方..依家租左間屋同居緊...<br />\n<br />\n6年嚟..我同B 都冇見過面..係間中會夢見佢..聽到某啲歌會諗起佢..有時會有少少衝動想搵佢..但係冇勇氣..<br />\n<br />\n直至兩個月前喺街見佢..之後whatsapp 左佢..同佢keep住whatsapp到依家..只係會傾啲無聊野..冇見出嚟過面..每次其實都係我主動搵佢..<br />\n<br />\n心裡面好想試下同佢一齊.. 一日半日都好..因為對佢..我有太多遺憾原來一直放唔開..<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我諗佢都冇咁嘅意思.. 同埋我知我實在唔應該咁樣諗..<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想搵人傾下..有冇人有類似經歷..?"},{"pid":"31474598dca24fa739e8362b3f6a443f39f141ca","tid":390194,"uid":116421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:23:50.000Z","msg":"慘..冇人理"},{"pid":"98dae48bcdba7fc1bd7426f677f740aa7bd5b5b7","tid":390194,"uid":116421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:24:28.000Z","msg":"我係咪好錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fe56e654ed9efd40e9088a2a79b46783b07293","tid":390194,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:31:52.000Z","msg":"判斷下呢個係錯覺定感覺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對佢可能因為無見太耐，而產生你好掛住佢既錯覺<br />\n<br />\n同埋你對女友感覺點先? 淡左? <br />\n一段愛情就係靠雙方維繫，可能你女友一直都努力維繫緊<br />\n所以如果你仲愛佢既，你就諗下自己黎緊點喇"},{"pid":"58b2c8c2195413c51a6f5e77a0f1943a3a7ae82f","tid":390194,"uid":116421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:12:33.000Z","msg":"係錯覺就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實.. 念念不忘都係因為我成日去諗<br />\n我唔去諗就冇野"},{"pid":"ed3fc1a7756eadc4cd11bebebdf532abe925a63f","tid":390194,"uid":4218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T11:03:37.000Z","msg":"樓主是個渣男 負皮上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac3e3afd06cacae6a1214b7e7fafbd862f12bcb","tid":390194,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T11:05:40.000Z","msg":"放過c啦好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee932103416029fbb7b0f7b2afad42c8bc04ad5","tid":390194,"uid":116421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:31:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放過c啦好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解唔係放開B ....<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77bbebc4a7ee20641778c1254111bee264ba9c1c","tid":390194,"uid":116421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主是個渣男 負皮上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TdAQ5nDKtIA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTdAQ5nDKtIA&d=%2BnNreoHSAT5xh0CxqRKFY8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f5c006ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TdAQ5nDKtIA</a>"},{"pid":"12e95944a2aed0353fafee0c3121af853d071dca","tid":390194,"uid":68088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:41:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>放過c啦好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解唔係放開B ....<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為你唔配有B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3680ebc014b2330af29b61f66f350057bc731e1","tid":390194,"uid":68088,"l